#account
  %div
    %fieldset
      %legend 加入會員
    Create an account to shop with HANCHOR! You will be able to check details and status of your orders. Your personal information won’t be shared with any others.
    %br
      %br
        加入本網站會員立即進行購物並可追蹤訂單，HANCHOR不會洩漏任何資料給第三方，除HANCHOR外，會員不會收到來自第三人之電子郵件。
        %br
          %br
            = link_to "註冊",register_path, class: 'button'
  %div
    %fieldset
      %legend 會員登入
    %br
    = form_tag '/login' do
      = label_tag "電子郵件:"
      = text_field_tag :username
      = label_tag "密碼: "
      = password_field_tag :password
      %br
      = submit_tag "登入", class: 'button'
      = link_to "忘記密碼","", class: 'button'
